); font-family: Söhne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Together, let\'s expand the horizons of possibility and create a world where compassion, justice, and sustainability thrive. Join us on the journey to shape a brighter tomorrow through Impact Horizons.</p>', 2, 'goal', 1, 0, 1, 'Apartment No. 34, Lake View Tower, Uttara Sector 3, Dhaka', 20, '2026-12-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqhNILVX8IE', '2024-02-17 04:36:23', '2024-05-04 11:23:12'),
(20, 'Cause Showcase: Elevate Your Impact with Featured Campaigns', 'cause-showcase-elevate-your-impact-with-featured-campaigns', 6, 22, '193997901714989290.jpg', 3008.99, 50560, '<p><strong>Description:</strong></p><p>Ignite change and spark hope with our collection of impactful initiatives! At our charity website, we believe in the power of collective action to bring about meaningful transformations in the world. Explore our diverse range of campaigns that address pressing issues and inspire hope for a better tomorrow.</p><p><strong>Here are some of the initiatives waiting for your support and involvement:</strong></p><ol><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Education Empowerment</strong><strong>:</strong> Help break the cycle of poverty by supporting education initiatives that provide access to quality learning opportunities for children and adults alike. From building schools to providing scholarships, every contribution makes a difference.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Community Resilience</strong><strong>: </strong>Strengthen communities and build resilience in the face of adversity. Support projects that focus on disaster preparedness, community infrastructure, and empowering local leaders to lead sustainable development efforts.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Heal the Planet</strong><strong>: </strong>Join the movement to protect our planet\'s precious ecosystems and biodiversity. Support reforestation efforts, sustainable agriculture projects, and initiatives aimed at combating climate change for a healthier, more sustainable future.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Empower Youth</strong><strong>: </strong>Invest in the next generation of leaders by supporting youth empowerment programs. From mentorship initiatives to skill-building workshops, these campaigns aim to equip young people with the tools and resources they need to thrive.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Healthcare Access for All</strong><strong>: </strong>Stand with us in advocating for universal healthcare access and support initiatives that provide essential medical care to underserved communities. Your support can help save lives and improve health outcomes for countless individuals.</li></ol><p><strong>How You Can Get Involved:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Donate: </strong>Your financial contributions directly support the programs and projects of each initiative, making a tangible impact on the ground.</li><li><strong>Volunteer:</strong> Get hands-on by volunteering your time and skills to support local projects and community-based initiatives.</li><li><strong>Advocate: </strong>Raise awareness about the issues addressed by our campaigns, advocate for policy changes, and amplify the voices of those in need.</li><li><strong>Connect:</strong> Join our community of changemakers, connect with like-minded individuals, and share ideas for creating positive change.</li></ul><p>Together, let\'s spark hope and create a brighter future for all. Explore our impactful initiatives, choose the ones that resonate with you, and join us in making a difference today!</p>', 1, 'goal', 1, 0, 0, 'House No. 45/B, Road No. 9, Uttara Sector 10, Dhaka, Bangladesh', 60500, '2026-12-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqhNILVX8IE', '2024-02-17 04:41:26', '2024-05-06 17:48:25'),
(21, 'Impact Unleashed: Explore Our Top Campaigns', 'impact-unleashed-explore-our-top-campaigns', 5, 22, '19355697681714796985.jpg', 52.49, 401.39, '<p><strong style=\"color: rgb(13, 13, 13);\">Description:</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Welcome to Impact Unleashed, where every action counts! Dive into our top campaigns that are making a significant difference in communities worldwide. These initiatives tackle critical issues head-on and are driven by passionate individuals like you who are committed to creating positive change.</p><p>Here are some of our top campaigns waiting for your support and involvement:</p><ol><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Empower Women</strong><strong>:</strong> Stand with us in empowering women and girls around the globe. Support initiatives that promote gender equality, provide education and economic opportunities, and advocate for women\'s rights in all aspects of life.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Feed the Hungry</strong><strong>: </strong>Help us combat hunger and food insecurity by supporting food banks, community kitchens, and sustainable agriculture projects. Your contribution can make a real difference in ensuring no one goes to bed hungry.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Build Sustainable Communities</strong><strong>:</strong> Join hands in building resilient and sustainable communities. Support projects that focus on renewable energy, eco-friendly infrastructure, and disaster preparedness to create a better future for all.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Protect Endangered Species</strong><strong>: </strong>Take a stand for wildlife conservation and biodiversity. Support initiatives that protect endangered species, preserve their habitats, and promote responsible stewardship of our planet\'s natural resources.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Mental Health Matters</strong><strong>:</strong> Break the stigma surrounding mental health and support initiatives that promote mental wellness, provide access to mental health resources, and offer support to those struggling with mental health challenges.</li></ol><p><strong>How You Can Make an Impact:</strong></p><ul><li>Donate: Your financial support directly funds the programs and projects of each campaign.</li><li>Volunteer: Get involved in hands-on activities, events, and outreach efforts organized by our partner organizations.</li><li>Advocate: Raise awareness, educate others, and advocate for policy changes to address the root causes of the issues tackled by our campaigns.</li><li>Engage: Participate in community discussions, share your stories, and connect with like-minded individuals who are passionate about making a difference.</li></ul><p>Together, we have the power to unleash positive change and create a brighter future for all. Explore our top campaigns, choose the ones that resonate with you, and join us on this impactful journey today!</p>', 1, 'goal', 1, 1, 0, 'House No. 23, Road No. 12/A, Uttara Sector 5, Dhaka, Bangladesh', 150, '2025-12-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqhNILVX8IE', '2024-02-17 04:43:20', '2024-05-06 17:48:20'),
(23, 'Campaigns on the Rise: Join Our Featured Movements', 'campaigns-on-the-rise-join-our-featured-movements', 8, 22, '631826971714797140.jpg', 0, 93451.78, '<p><strong>Description:</strong></p><p>Join us in making a difference! Our charity website is proud to present a collection of featured movements that are making waves in communities around the world. These campaigns address pressing issues and inspire change, and now is your chance to get involved. Whether you\'re passionate about environmental sustainability, social justice, education, or health, there\'s something for everyone in our diverse selection of campaigns.</p><p><strong>Here\'s a glimpse into some of our featured movements:</strong></p><ol><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Clean Up Our Oceans</strong><strong>: </strong>Help us combat plastic pollution and protect marine life by participating in beach clean-ups, supporting policies to reduce single-use plastics, and promoting sustainable alternatives.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Equality for All</strong><strong>:</strong> Stand up against discrimination and inequality by supporting initiatives that promote equal rights and opportunities regardless of gender, race, sexual orientation, or socio-economic background.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Education for Every Child</strong><strong>:</strong> Join hands with us to ensure that every child has access to quality education. Support schools in underserved communities, provide scholarships, or volunteer as a mentor to empower the next generation.</li><li><strong style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Health and Wellness</strong><strong>:</strong> Advocate for better healthcare access and support initiatives that promote mental health awareness, disease prevention, and healthy living habits for all.</li><li><span style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);\">Climate Action Now</span>: Take action against climate change by supporting renewable energy projects, tree planting initiatives, and advocating for sustainable living practices.</li></ol><p><strong>How You Can Get Involved:</strong></p><ul><li>Donate: Your contributions directly support the initiatives and projects of each featured movement.</li><li>Volunteer: Join hands-on activities, events, and programs organized by our partner organizations.</li><li>Spread the Word: Share these campaigns on social media, raise awareness, and inspire others to join the cause.</li><li>Take Action: Sign petitions, participate in rallies, and engage in advocacy efforts to drive positive change.</li></ul><p>Together, we can amplify these movements and create a better world for future generations. Join us today and be a part of something meaningful!</p>', 0, 'goal', 1, 1, 0, 'House No. 23, Road No. 12/A, Uttara Sector 5, Dhaka, Bangladesh', 2050, '2025-03-02', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqhNILVX8IE', '2024-03-10 04:58:02', '2024-05-06 17:12:45');
