(487, 62, 'How does your charity support LGBTQ+ youth who may be experiencing homelessness or facing rejection from their families?', 'Supporting LGBTQ+ youth who may be experiencing homelessness or facing rejection from their families is a priority for us at [Charity Name]. We offer safe and affirming spaces where LGBTQ+ youth can access resources and support'),
