(45, 38, 'TKT67131545', 22, NULL, 'Hey,\r\n\r\nJust wanted to send a quick reminder that you are capable of achieving anything you set your mind to. I know self-doubt can creep in sometimes, but don\'t let it overshadow your potential.\r\n\r\nYou have unique talents and strengths that make you truly remarkable. Embrace them, and trust in your ability to overcome any obstacle that comes your way.\r\n\r\nBelieve in yourself, because I believe in you.\r\n\r\nTake care,\r\nYour Name', NULL, '2024-05-06 16:05:24', '2024-05-06 16:05:24'),
