(47, 39, 'TKT59473885', 22, NULL, 'Hi,\r\nI know you\'re going through a tough time right now, but I want you to know that you\'re not alone. You have the strength and resilience to weather this storm and emerge even stronger on the other side.\r\n\r\nIt\'s okay to feel overwhelmed sometimes, but don\'t let it consume you. Take things one step at a time, and remember to be kind to yourself along the way.\r\n\r\nYou\'re capable of amazing things, and I have every confidence that you\'ll come out of this stronger than ever.\r\n\r\nKeep pushing forward!\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\nYour Name', NULL, '2024-05-06 16:07:39', '2024-05-06 16:07:39'),
(48, 40, 'TKT46565939', 22, NULL, 'Hey,\r\n\r\nJust a quick note to remind you of the warrior within you. You\'ve faced challenges head-on before, and you\'ve always emerged victorious. I know things might seem tough right now, but you have the resilience and strength to overcome anything that comes your way.\r\n\r\nStay focused on your goals, and don\'t let anything deter you from achieving them. You\'re capable of greatness, and I have no doubt that you\'ll achieve everything you set your mind to.\r\n\r\nKeep fighting, keep pushing forward, and remember that I\'m here cheering you on every step of the way.\r\n\r\nTake care,\r\n[Your Name]', NULL, '2024-05-06 16:08:27', '2024-05-06 16:08:27'),
(49, 41, 'TKT39394362', 22, NULL, 'Hello there,\r\n\r\nIn the midst of life\'s ups and downs, it\'s essential to recognize the transformative power of challenges. Each obstacle we face is an opportunity for growth, a chance to test our limits, and a pathway to becoming the best version of ourselves.\r\n\r\nI want to remind you today of your incredible resilience and strength. You\'ve navigated through turbulent waters before, and each time, you\'ve emerged stronger and more resilient than before. Your ability to face adversity head-on is truly remarkable.\r\n\r\nAs you encounter challenges on your journey, remember that they are not roadblocks but stepping stones. Embrace them with courage and determination, knowing that they are shaping you into the person you are meant to become.\r\n\r\nEven when the path ahead seems uncertain, have faith in your abilities and trust in the process. You possess within you an unwavering spirit, capable of overcoming any obstacle that comes your way.\r\n\r\nSo, keep moving forward with unwavering determination, knowing that with each step you take, you\'re inching closer to your goals. Embrace the challenges, embrace the growth, and embrace the incredible journey that is life.\r\n\r\nYou\'ve got this, and I believe in you every step of the way.\r\n\r\nWarmest regards,\r\nYour Name', NULL, '2024-05-06 16:09:35', '2024-05-06 16:09:35'),
(50, 42, 'TKT12790484', 22, NULL, 'Greetings,\r\n\r\nIn the midst of life\'s tempests, it\'s easy to feel overwhelmed by the crashing waves of adversity. Yet, within you lies a reservoir of strength and resilience, waiting to be tapped into during times of trial.\r\n\r\nI\'m reaching out today to offer a gentle reminder of your remarkable ability to weather storms. Like a sturdy ship navigating rough seas, you have the capacity to endure even the fiercest of challenges with courage and grace.\r\n\r\nThough the journey may be arduous at times, never doubt your capacity to rise above the turbulence. With each wave you face, you gain valuable insights, hone your skills, and emerge all the more resilient.\r\n\r\nRemember, it\'s okay to seek shelter in the midst of a storm, to pause and gather your strength before pressing forward. You are not alone on this journey; there are countless souls cheering you on, ready to offer support when needed.\r\n\r\nSo, as you navigate the storms of life, hold steadfast to the knowledge that you possess the resilience to overcome any obstacle that crosses your path. Embrace the challenges as opportunities for growth, and let your indomitable spirit guide you toward calmer shores.\r\n\r\nKeep faith in yourself and your abilities, for you are stronger than you know.\r\n\r\nWith warmest wishes,\r\n[Your Name]', NULL, '2024-05-06 16:10:25', '2024-05-06 16:10:25'),
